

     
         Something about IIFM to prospective students      Many students while coming to iifm have many qualms and don't know whom to approach for the same.They don't have an idea what iifm is all about.IIFM is not a conventional B school.Its a institute which has been specially designed to cater to the environmental and developmental sector.That's why It has been heavily susidised and i believe its the only institute which provides stipend to its students.The campus is very serene and full of lush greenery.The no. of students are very less and the facilities unique e.g. library and computer centre.Our alumnis are working in top notch organisations like  World bank,PWC ,etc.At the moment multi clubs have been made like Cultural club,Movie club,literary club etc.And each club is working to its potential to make the campus vibrant.The hostel is very spacious and the food very salubrious.The faculties are very cooperative and hardworking.Regular field trips are being organised to facilitate students to juxtapose their theory with hands on practical experience.The students have to undergo a diurnal tight schedule which is very grilling and makes them disciplined,teamworker and competitive,but at the same time it's fun.At iifm you also get the feeling that you have actually contributed something back to society and mother earth.    So for next year i wish to say good luck to all of students who want to make to iifm       Ranjan Kumar         PFM 2006 IIFM      
     
    
